J. W. MORRIS et al., Appellants, v. Raphael DECHTER et al., Appellees. No. 11316. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit Nov. 22, 1946. Frank L. Kostlan, of Pasadena, Cal., for appellants. B. L. Hoyt and Dechter, Hoyt, Pines & Walsh, all of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellees R. D. Decther, D. Decther, D. H. Graham, and Mrs. D. H. Graham.

Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS, and ORR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed.
